# MoonBark Godot Projects — Monorepo

## Structure
```
C:\gamedev\godot\projects\        ← monorepo root (git shell + submodules)
  cores/                           ← shared core libraries
    MoonBark.Framework/             ← main framework (main branch)
    MoonBark.ECS/                  ← ECS implementation (main branch)
  plugins/                         ← Godot plugins (25 repos)
    AI/, Abilities/, Attributes/, AudioSystem/, EcsPhysics2D/, ...
  games/                          ← game projects
    moonbark-idle/                 ← idle game (master branch)
    thistletide/                   ← main game (master branch)
```

## Branch Conventions
- `cores/` repos: `main` branch
- `plugins/` repos: `main` branch (most), `master` (some older ones)
- `games/` repos: `master` branch

## Common Commands
```bash
# Status of all submodules
git submodule status

# Update monorepo pointers after submodule changes
git add cores/ plugins/ games/
git commit -m "submodule: sync pointers"
git push origin main

# Health audit
python3 ~/.hermes/scripts/audit_golden_trio.py C:\gamedev\godot\projects
```

## Code Standards
- All MoonBark value classes: `IEquatable<T>` — no exceptions
- ECS types in `ECS/` subdirectory only (plugins)
- Godot C#: unsubscribe in `_ExitTree()`, null Actions in `Dispose()`
- Golden trio: `HEALTH.md`, `README.md`, `ROADMAP.md` in every repo

## Health Audit (Golden Trio v3)
Format each repo's HEALTH.md with:
```
# [RepoName] — One-line description
## Status: Active | Stale | WIP | Archived | Wrecked
## Last Audited: YYYY-MM-DD
## Discovered Issues
(none yet)
## Metrics
- Lines of C# production code: N
- Test coverage: N%
- .csproj count: N
- Last commit: YYYY-MM-DD — short description
## Architecture
## Dependencies
(none)
```
